::Starlight/Slayer::

Starlight stops firing when Prebon goes under. She flies off to the 
Iron Fist for repairs.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Slayer exits the CR chamber, fully repaired. He walks over to the 
computer.

"Computer, initate search for Commander Prebon," he says, waiting for 
the computer to do as ordered.
